room_title: Escape room "Cabin in the Woods" by The Great Escape in Cameron
room_description:
Your journalism agency has received a tip regarding the whereabouts of an active serial killer with a passion for the arts, especially photography. You're eager to confirm this lead, warn the authorities and write an exclusive story. But you know this kind of investigation can prove dangerous, so you recruit a team of your brave colleagues to come along.
It turns out your gut feeling was correct. But you weren't the only one tipped off. Now the killer is chasing you through his forest, luring you to his cabin. Will your instincts be enough to save you and your team this time?
